How to run node application using PM2 manager:

=========================================
RUN COMMAND
=========================================
pm2 start npm --name "your-app-name" -- start
-----------------------------------------
EXAMPLE
-----------------------------------------
pm2 start npm --name "AREAX_CORE_API" -- start
=========================================
RUN COMMAND: CLUSTER
=========================================
pm2 start npm --name "your-app-name" -- start -i 2
-----------------------------------------
pm2 start npm --name "AREAX_CORE_API" -- start -i 2
-----------------------------------------
